Package: rowSum
Title: Row Sums via Rust and Faer
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Suryansh", "Dey", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "suryansh@example.com")
Description: A minimal R package that passes a dense matrix to Rust via extendr,
    computes row sums using the faer linear algebra crate, and returns the result.
    Demonstrates the extendr R-to-Rust FFI for the hyperSpec GSoC medium test.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
SystemRequirements: Cargo (Rust's package manager), rustc
